text: Paweł Gawron (23 March 1921 - 1 October 1983) was a Polish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Rydułtowy
